ing: 1 (1.25 ounce) package dry taco seasoning mix
des: "This recipe is easy, yet delicious when used in tacos or other Mexican cuisine. Try it for enchiladas and nachos too."
ins:
Mix chicken broth and taco seasoning in a bowl.
Place chicken breasts in a slow cooker and pour chicken broth mixture over chicken.
Cover and cook on Low for 6 to 8 hours.
Shred chicken to serve.
